    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aquatint process in which a salt solution is used to lift the ground, and exposes the image areas so the plate can be etched.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
